1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,286
The railway station building
has not been used
for many years.

2
00:00:04,286 --> 00:00:08,571
But trains still stop here.

3
00:00:08,571 --> 00:00:12,857
From here you can travel
to Wrocław,

4
00:00:12,857 --> 00:00:17,143
or the other way
to Oborniki Śląskie

5
00:00:17,143 --> 00:00:21,429
and farther
to Poznań.

6
00:00:21,429 --> 00:00:25,714
This railway line
was built
over 150 years ago,

7
00:00:25,714 --> 00:00:30,000
in the year 1856.

8
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:34,286
But Pęgów did not get
its station right away.

9
00:00:34,286 --> 00:00:38,571
It was built
50 years later,
in 1905.

10
00:00:38,571 --> 00:00:42,857
Back then, trains
were very important.

11
00:00:42,857 --> 00:00:47,143
Cars were slow,
often broken,

12
00:00:47,143 --> 00:00:51,429
and only rich people
could afford them.

13
00:00:51,429 --> 00:00:55,714
Thanks to the railway,
Pęgów became

14
00:00:55,714 --> 00:01:00,000
a trip destination
for people from Wrocław.

15
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:04,286
Several tourist routes
were created.

16
00:01:04,286 --> 00:01:08,571
One led to Wilczyn
through a lovely forest.

17
00:01:08,571 --> 00:01:12,857
A lot has changed
in 100 years,

18
00:01:12,857 --> 00:01:17,143
but Wilczyn is still
great for trips.

19
00:01:17,143 --> 00:01:21,429
There are beautiful
relaxing areas
by the water.

20
00:01:21,429 --> 00:01:25,714
Walking through the forest,
you can follow

21
00:01:25,714 --> 00:01:30,000
the Chestnut Avenue —
rare trees in a forest!